# @cumulus/lzards-api-client

## Lzards Api Client

The Level Zero and Repositories Data Store (LZARDS) is the "backup of last resort" for 
cloud-native missions and datasets, should the AWS-hosted data become inaccessible for any reason, 
including government policy, breach of contract, financial outage, or catastrophic vendor failure.

## Usage

```js
npm install @cumulus/lzards-api-client
```

